I"p<p>MessItUp is an University project to discourage food wastage and enable hostellers to clearly express opinions on food quality. It is currently being developed as a mobile app (Android supported currently).</p>

<p>The modules proposed to be implemented include:</p>
<ol>
  <li>Viewing of the mess food menu - and learn about the values of each item</li>
  <li>Inputting the opinion of whether an individual will be visiting the mess at a particular time of the day</li>
  <li>Inputting feedback on food quality by an individual for a particular time of the day</li>
  <li>Data-driven analytics to provide real-time recommendation on when to visit mess depending upon crowd</li>
  <li>Data-driven seat allocation to provide tentative suggestions on taking up seats in order to reduce chaos and confusion
<br />
<img src="https://i.imgur.com/oZ43LVWl.png" /></li>
</ol>

